{"tid":1365554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再繼暗黑兵法] 群眾鬥群眾","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:46:28.000Z","uid":5489,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f2ca6171ada5251c47686587230b516bc4ab82","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:19:57.000Z","msg":"上次出左篇文 俾大家屌鳩虎頭蛇尾<br />\n希望大家明白 暗黑兵法 講太明 就冇撚用<br />\n<br />\n今次只講重點<br />\n<br />\n1. 元朗727<br />\n<br />\n上文講過，元朗恐襲是為港共現時為止行得最錯既一步，反效果亦最大。<br />\n但一個將近窮途末路既政府，呢一刻唯有繼續撐落去，若果成功引發到一場大型群眾集體械鬥，自然造就一個機會將示威者一舉殲滅，甚至justify 戒嚴同解放軍。<br />\n你話冇可能，一出呢兩招即焦土。<br />\n錯了，只要引爆到一場真暴動，即使會有後遺症，亦已經減到最低，因為呢場真暴動為更高層次武力提供左正當性。<br />\n<br />\n所以727當日一定要和平！！！<br />\n受到襲擊當然必定要自衛，但切忌打到性起，令自己變做元朗恐襲當晚既白衫暴徒！<br />\n<br />\n2. 運動前路<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，其實港共已無退路，可以打得既牌都打到盡。<br />\n除左避免我上面講既情況出現令佢有機會翻身，亦可以同時做其他野加速 港共 黑警 鄉黑 滅亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">兄弟爬山</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">各有各做</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不篤灰不割席</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0614ad2747fae2b3656d78e3d722d310dcd15266","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<br />\n戰略分析 今次真係成場運動最關鍵一步 請巴打聽細佬一言 入內討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355350\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355350</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2bb861f4c7d05b66155780d33a95d7b143e9fc8e","tid":1365554,"uid":290145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"劇本：黑社會一定龜縮，警方視遊行人士為非法集結，結果示威者vs警察衝突"},{"pid":"0771094e7cd9da4b76130b885fd731913a6c5d4c","tid":1365554,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee92b752fe244608d11a9dcc6fafb477f840897","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0771094e7cd9da4b76130b885fd731913a6c5d4c","tid":1365554,"uid":41458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9644a2ec5132728f8abe1aa281f5b2f50f2393fe","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:33:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"366538491721f63ff2013d2c2e8c1f4c8f84abbd","tid":1365554,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"第二招堅揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9873274f7fb28ff6e0b7f2e7712007f2e86908ed","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"366538491721f63ff2013d2c2e8c1f4c8f84abbd","tid":1365554,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:34:01.000Z","msg":"第二招堅揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce468de5d70af81088db336abf7ff70354a848d","tid":1365554,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3ff3090d6d8900fb2f305d1ed9505bdf